// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0014 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 930e994e-5363-5958-a643-6147527b3ca4

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
